net.sf.saxon.trace

Interface TraceableComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Locatable, Traceable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GlobalParam, GlobalVariable, MemoFunction, NamedTemplate, StreamableUserFunction, TemplateRule, TemplateRuleEE, UndeclaredVariable, UserFunction, XQueryExpression, XQueryExpressionEE

    public interface TraceableComponent
extends Traceable
    A construct whose execution can be notified to a TraceListener. In practice this is a function or template or global variable.
